Nollywood actress and ‘The Johnsons’ star, Ada Ameh’s daughter, Aladi Godgifts Ameh, is dead. Aladi died on Tuesday, October 20, 2020. The Benue-born actress, who confirmed the death on her Instagram page, expressed sadness over her daughter’s death. She wrote, “Fams!!! My lovely people. Pray for me, my beautiful darling child chose to go and be with the Lord early hours of today. “Aladi Godgifts Ameh@lalas_touch why did you choose to leave me now? Ladi how you want make I do na? “I will be strong !! GOD Has to help me.”